@startuml
title State diagram of the system operations of "Process Sale"

[*] --> WaitingForSale

state "Waiting for a new sale" as WaitingForSale
state "Enter items one by one" as EnterItems
state "Move to payment" as MoveToPayment
state "Complete sale" as CompleteSale
state "Return to waiting" as ReturnToWaiting

WaitingForSale --> EnterItems : new sale
EnterItems --> EnterItems : add item
EnterItems --> MoveToPayment : end of sale
MoveToPayment --> CompleteSale : cash payment
MoveToPayment --> CompleteSale : card or check payment
CompleteSale --> CompleteSale : payment approved
CompleteSale --> ReturnToWaiting : payment finished

@enduml
